## ガウス積分
### \\(\int e^{-ax^2} dx\\)
\\[
  \begin{align}
	\int ^{\infty} _{-\infty} e^{-ax^2} dx &= \sqrt{\frac{\pi}{a}} \\\\
	\int ^{\infty} _{0} e^{-ax^2} dx &= \frac{1}{2}\sqrt{\frac{\pi}{a}}
  \end{align}
\\]
- 証明  
  \\(I = \int ^{\infty} _{0} e^{-ax^2} dx\\)と置く,
  \\[
  \begin{align}
  I^2 &= \left(\int ^{\infty} _{0} e^{-ax^2} dx\right)^2 \\\\
  &= \left(\int ^{\infty} _{0} e^{-ax^2} dx\right)\left(\int ^{\infty} _{0} e^{-ay^2} dy\right) \\\\
  &= \int ^{\infty} _{0} e^{-a(x^2+y^2)} dx
  \end{align}
  \\]
